data.description: Surrounded by million dollar homes  Westwood Estates is a hidden Wesley Chapel gem where you can stretch out and  bring your horses, yet be close to major highways, shopping, dining and  recreational fun. MOTIVATED sellers ready to sell, this home can be used as a great investment property too! You can have peaceful country living and still be  close to everywhere you need to be, all in a GATED Equestrian community with  larger homesites, giving you privacy while still enjoying an abundance of nature.  Located on a quiet cul-de-sac, this 5 bedroom/4 bath PLUS LOFT  home has all the features you are looking for. Walking through the double front  doors with leaded glass windows, you are greeted with expansive views from all the  main living areas making a seamless transition from inside to out. Family living and  entertaining is a dream with the easy flow of the living, dining, and family rooms all  adjacent to the kitchen. But the heart of this home is the kitchen, where memories  will be made as you pull up a comfy stool to the breakfast bar or settle into the  breakfast niche to start your day off sharing coffee with family, or prepare for  special holidays or weekend gatherings of family and friends. Turning out gourmet  delights will be easy in this kitchen featuring rich Maple cabinets with accent glass  doors, granite countertops with easy to clean granite backsplashes, stainless  appliances, and convenient cookware drawers under the cooktop, all while staying  visually integrated into the main living areas so everyone is a part of all the activity.  In its own private wing, the primary 25’ x 13’ bedroom is your oasis from the world.  There is plenty of space including an extended seating area with outdoor access to  the lanai, tray ceilings, and dual walk-in closets flows into the large ensuite bath  featuring an oversized tub, separate shower, 2 separate chest vanities. Right next  to the owner’s suite is another private bedroom perfect for so many different uses  and is across from a full bath; make it an office, craft room, extra bedroom, baby  nursery, or exercise room. You decide! On the other side of the home are two more  bedrooms with a hall bath, the laundry room, and stairs going up to the second  floor. Here you will find a private loft area with a door that includes a separate bedroom and  bathroom making it a perfect area for family casual living, a Nanny suite, in-law  living, or a guest retreat. All this indoor living is enhanced by the expansive  outdoor living and views this property provides. For starters, you can let the cares  of the day float away as you enjoy the 7 person jacuzzi spa complete with a  waterfall light show and Bose surround sound speakers. But you won’t want to  miss the fresh pizza as it comes pipping hot from your fire brick pizza oven. And  set up the outdoor games. There is room for all of it. Just imagine all the weekend  fun you can have. Even “Rover” will be thrilled with the large dog house with AC!  Vinyl fencing and horse fencing was added in 2022 and there is plenty of room to  add a pool, another garage, or stable. Additional features include an energy  efficient 50-panel solar system to cut down on energy bills, plus a water softener  and water filtration system added in 2022. Close to major travel access (I-75, SR  54 and SR 52) and Wiregrass Mall, Tampa Premium Outlets, KRATE, COSTCO and  more! Call today to view this spectacular property!
